ia Getty Images）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Spotify-logo.-Credit-Photo-by-Dilara-Irem-Sancar_Anadolu-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Spotify-logo.-Credit-Photo-by-Dilara-Irem-Sancar_Anadolu-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Spotify-logo.-Credit-Photo-by-Dilara-Irem-Sancar_Anadolu-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Spotify-logo.-Credit-Photo-by-Dilara-Irem-Sancar_Anadolu-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Spotify-logo.-Credit-Photo-by-Dilara-Irem-Sancar_Anadolu-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Spotify-logo.-Credit-Photo-by-Dilara-Irem-Sancar_Anadolu-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/spotify">Spotify</a>已开始从流媒体平台上删除支持乌克兰战争的俄罗斯艺术家。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/artists-music-2023-challenges-2024-hopes-streaming-gigs-payment-blur-easy-life-cherise-lvra-get-cape-fac-3565687">艺术家谈 2023 年的挑战和 2024 年的希望：“我只想看到我们通过销售唱片获得报酬”</a></strong></li></ul><p>早在 2022 年，Spotify <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spotify-shutters-russian-ofifce-indefinitely-invasion-ukraine-3174021">就关闭了莫斯科办事处，以应对俄罗斯持续入侵乌克兰</a>。该流媒体平台确认其莫斯科办事处将“无限期”关闭，并表示他们正在“为我们在莫斯科的人员”以及“乌克兰员工的全球社区”提供个人支持。</p><p>在俄罗斯出台新立法后，他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spotify-reportedly-set-to-suspend-its-service-in-russia-3190786">暂停了在该国的服务</a>，该立法规定报告任何可能抹黑俄罗斯军队的事件都是非法的。</p><p>该公司在一份声明中表示：“Spotify 始终认为，努力保持我们在俄罗斯的服务运营，以提供来自该地区的可信、独立的新闻和信息至关重要。”</p><p>现在，该流媒体平台已开始删除支持战争的俄罗斯艺术家的个人资料 - 完全删除他们的音乐。 </p><figure id="attachment_3771490" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3771490" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3771490" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Spotify-image.-Credit-Photo-by-Nikolas-Kokovlis_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="2024 年 5 月 20 日，Spotify 徽标显示在希腊雅典的智能手机屏幕和电脑屏幕上。（摄影：Nikolas Kokovlis/NurPhoto via Getty Images）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Spotify-image.-Credit-Photo-by-Nikolas-Kokovlis_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Spotify-image.-Credit-Photo-by-Nikolas-Kokovlis_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Spotify-image.-Credit-Photo-by-Nikolas-Kokovlis_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Spotify-image.-Credit-Photo-by-Nikolas-Kokovlis_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Spotify-image.-Credit-Photo-by-Nikolas-Kokovlis_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Spotify-image.-Credit-Photo-by-Nikolas-Kokovlis_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3771490" class="wp-caption-text"> 2024 年 5 月 20 日，Spotify 徽标显示在希腊雅典的智能手机屏幕和电脑屏幕上。（摄影：Nikolas Kokovlis/NurPhoto via Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>据<a href="https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2024/06/28/spotify-removes-songs-of-pro-war-russian-artists-a85550" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《莫斯科时报》</em></a>报道，Spotify 选择将支持战争的俄罗斯艺术家从其服务中撤出，从而影响了 Lyube、Grigory Leps、Oleg Gazmanov、Polina Gagarina 和 Shaman 等乐队。</p><p> Spotify 在发给该出版物的一份声明中表示：“平台规则明确规定，当我们发现明显违反我们的内容政策或当地法律的内容时，我们将采取行动。经审查，这些艺术家已达到下架门槛。”</p><p>该主播没有继续具体说明哪些内容违反了他们的政策。自 2022 年俄罗斯政府入侵乌克兰以来，一些受到该流媒体决定将其目录从平台上撤下的影响的艺术家一直受到欧盟制裁。</p><p>加加林娜和萨满最近出现在布鲁塞尔上周的制裁计划中（Per <a href="https://www.stereogum.com/2270171/spotify-removes-russian-artists-who-support-ukraine-war/news/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Stereogum</em></a> ），名单上写着萨满“多次参加克里姆林宫组织的音乐会，包括克里姆林宫为那场战争举行的周年纪念活动，并在乌克兰非法占领地区举办音乐会。 ”</p><p>而加加林娜据称从国家赞助的庆祝吞并莫斯科部分控制下的乌克兰地区的活动中“获得了大量收入”。</p><p>在 Spotify 的其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/deadmau5-considering-removing-music-from-spotify-after-daniel-eks-comments-fucking-vultures-3769054">Deadmau5 最近公开反对该平台，此前首席执行官 Daniel Ek 上个月就“创建内容”的成本发表了评论。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spotify-removes-russian-artists-who-support-ukraine-war-3771472">Spotify 删除支持乌克兰战争的俄罗斯艺术家的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 《发展受阻》主演马丁·马尔去世，享年 80 岁https://www.nme.com/news/arrested-development-star-martin-mull-dies-ged-80-3771148?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=arrested-development-star-martin-mull-dies-ged- 80Elizabeth Aubrey Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:23:08 +0000 Film NewsNewsTV News.. https://www.nme.com/?p=3771148 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Martin-Mull-Photo-by-Mat-Hayward_Getty-Images-for-Netflix.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="马丁·马尔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Martin-Mull-Photo-by-Mat-Hayward_Getty-Images-for-Netflix.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Martin-Mull-Photo-by-Mat-Hayward_Getty-Images-for-Netflix-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Martin-Mull-Photo-by-Mat-Hayward_Getty-Images-for-Netflix-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Martin-Mull-Photo-by-Mat-Hayward_Getty-Images-for-Netflix-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Martin-Mull-Photo-by-Mat-Hayward_Getty-Images-for-Netflix-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Martin-Mull-Photo-by-Mat-Hayward_Getty-Images-for-Netflix-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “从各个意义上来说，他都是一位真正的艺术家”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/arrested-development-star-martin-mull-dies-aged-80-3771148">《发展受阻》后的主演马丁·马尔去世，享年 80 岁，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Martin-Mull-Photo-by-Mat-Hayward_Getty-Images-for-Netflix.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="马丁·马尔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Martin-Mull-Photo-by-Mat-Hayward_Getty-Images-for-Netflix.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Martin-Mull-Photo-by-Mat-Hayward_Getty-Images-for-Netflix-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Martin-Mull-Photo-by-Mat-Hayward_Getty-Images-for-Netflix-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Martin-Mull-Photo-by-Mat-Hayward_Getty-Images-for-Netflix-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Martin-Mull-Photo-by-Mat-Hayward_Getty-Images-for-Netflix-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Martin-Mull-Photo-by-Mat-Hayward_Getty-Images-for-Netflix-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>演员兼喜剧演员马丁·马尔 (Martin Mull) 去世，享年 80 岁，他因出演情景喜剧《<i><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/arrested-development">发展受阻》</a> 、《少女女巫萨布丽娜》</i>和<i>《罗莎妮》</i>而闻名。</p><p>据他的女儿玛吉·马尔 (Maggie Mull) 称，这位演员在“与长期疾病进行了勇敢的斗争”后于上周四（6 月 27 日）在家中去世。</p><p>玛吉在 Instagram 上悼念，写道：“我的父亲在与长期病魔进行了英勇的斗争后，于 6 月 27 日在家中去世，我心碎不已。</p><p> “他因在所有可以想象到的创意领域表现出色以及为红屋顶酒店拍摄广告而闻名。他会觉得这个笑话很有趣。他从来都不好笑。他的妻子和女儿、他的朋友和同事、其他艺术家、喜剧演员和音乐家，以及许许多多的狗都会深深地思念我的父亲——这是一个真正杰出的人的标志。我非常爱他。”</p><p>马丁的一次突破出现在 1976 年，他在讽刺肥皂剧《<i>玛丽·哈特曼》</i>中扮演加斯·金布尔 (Garth Gimble)。他还出演了该剧的另外两部衍生剧，其中包括<i>《Fernwood 2 Nights》。</i>在此之前，他作为词曲作者和音乐喜剧演员获得了突破，在 70 年代为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frank-zappa">Frank Zappa</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-springsteen">Bruce Springsteen</a>开场。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C8xtnPPyeAH/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: